{"tid":1316813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「Fight Culb研討會」打交黎一膽二力三功夫","createTime":"2019-07-14T16:47:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T17:43:47.000Z","uid":156914,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"db35f9f94a180cc260095f67f86927768904d19e","tid":1316813,"uid":156914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:47:26.000Z","msg":"我識有啲人，佢地成日畀人恰畀人圍，佢地想反抗，但總係無辦法衝破心理關口去郁手。次次唔係退到去牆角，就係傻仔咁企係到畀人包圍<br />\n<br />\n為左拯救各位懦夫，我決定係到成立Fight Club<br />\n<br />\n本會旨左提升各參與者膽量，於臨危時不亂，挺身捍衛自己及同伴。<br />\n<br />\n本會之活動以實戰實踐，適應在危機下的情況<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"327b495cd11e3bb168c0e26239f11e0b628d3470","tid":1316813,"uid":156914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:47:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"48b3f4d581416b5ce9682e8388b70a4555d51c02","tid":1316813,"uid":156914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:47:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d4ac91a8443fc5fe63bc6232d82e2f857949b218","tid":1316813,"uid":156914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:51:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"632217fb3b2f0f7a0bc5fb052b271be4bfaf4322","tid":1316813,"uid":156914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:51:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7aa189dffc31154380b71db86da996b62b2e59cc","tid":1316813,"uid":156914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:01:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5de2b17570fd72ddd53ca2e45ad9f814dad638df","tid":1316813,"uid":156914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:05:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f8c51dc257b3a83acba8667c812332571191db67","tid":1316813,"uid":156914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:13:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5fb15634e24716d2ea6affcd5118c94b5a02c74e","tid":1316813,"uid":156914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:15:41.000Z","msg":"推"